OL,6,FThe two men in charge of navigating
OL,7,Fthe Commodore Goodwill Condor Ferry
OL,8,Fonly sounded its horn four to five
OL,9,Fseconds before a collision which
OL,10,Fkilled three fishermen, Jersey's Royal
OL,11,FCourt has been told.
OL,13,FContinuing their opening statement,
OL,14,Fthe prosecution argue that the actions
OL,15,Fof Lewis Peter Carr from Sunderland
OL,16,Fand Artur Sevash-Zade, a Ukrainian
OL,17,Fnational, caused the deaths of Larry
OL,18,FSimyunn, Jervis Baligat and Michael
OL,19,FMichieli, who were on board the much
OL,20,Fsmaller L'Ecume II vessel.
