OL,3,CFerry horn only sounded seconds before
OL,4,Cdeadly impact, court told
OL,6,FCrown Advocate Matthew Maletroit
OL,7,Fargues that Mr Carr put the ferry on a
OL,8,F"collision course" with the L'Ecume II
OL,9,Fand his actions were "incredibly
OL,10,Freckless".
OL,12,FThe prosecutor says both defendants
OL,13,Fwere "grossly negligent" and the
OL,14,Fcollision in December 2022 was
OL,15,F"already inevitable" by the time Mr
OL,16,FCarr made a last-minute effort to
OL,17,Favoid a crash.
