OL,6,FAn audio recording from the command
OL,7,Fdeck of the Condor Ferry before,
OL,8,Fduring and after impact was played in
OL,9,Fcourt.
OL,11,FAt around 5:05am on Thursday 8
OL,12,FDecember 2022, a man can be heard
OL,13,Ftelling another man he can go for
OL,14,Fbreakfast.
OL,16,FAdvocate Maletroit says this is Mr
OL,17,FCarr telling Mr Sevash-Zade to leave
OL,18,Fhis post, which he did for ten to 15
OL,19,Fminutes.
