OL,6,FThe prosecutor says this is "extremely
OL,7,Fbad practice" as Mr Sevash-Zade was
OL,8,Fthe sole lookout on duty and "totally
OL,9,Funnecessary" as he had only just got
OL,10,Fon shift.
OL,12,FAt 5:24am, Advocate Maletroit states
OL,13,Fthe ferry makes a turn which puts it
OL,14,Fin line with the L'Ecume II and Mr
OL,15,FCarr's adjustment using the autopilot
OL,16,Fwheel to avoid the vessel "made things
OL,17,Fworse".
