OL,3,CFerry horn only sounded seconds before
OL,4,Cdeadly impact, court told
OL,6,FThe prosecutor says Mr Carr was
OL,7,Fdistracted by pre-arrival preparations
OL,8,Fand paperwork, failing to mention
OL,9,Fanything of concern to the captain
OL,10,Fwhen he spoke to him before the
OL,11,Fcollision.
OL,13,FA man is heard saying, "Is this
OL,14,Ff****** guy sleeping?" moments before
OL,15,Fthe collision, which the prosecution
OL,16,Fimplied was Mr Sevash-Zade referring
OL,17,Fto the L'Ecume II vessel and the only
OL,18,Ftime he raised concern, despite
OL,19,Fearlier warnings.
