OL,3,CFerry horn only sounded seconds before
OL,4,Cdeadly impact, court told
OL,6,FThe ferry's horn can then be heard
OL,7,Fblasting eight times, four to five
OL,8,Fseconds before the impact at 5:35am.
OL,10,FFollowing the collision, Advocate
OL,11,FMaletroit says he would have expected
OL,12,FMr Carr and Mr Sevash-Zade to reduce
OL,13,Fspeed, turn back to the scene of the
OL,14,Fcollision, call the captain and report
OL,15,Fthe incident to the authorities.
OL,17,FHowever, instead, the prosecutor says
OL,18,Fthe ferry corrected course and
OL,19,Fcontinued towards St Helier.
