OL,6,FAdvocate Maletroit states that the
OL,7,Fcollision was felt in other areas of
OL,8,Fthe ship and crew members told Mr Carr
OL,9,Fto contact the Coast Guard.
OL,11,FThat phone call, four minutes after
OL,12,Fthe moment of impact, was played in
OL,13,Fcourt.
OL,15,FA man, whom the prosecution say is Mr
OL,16,FCarr, can be heard saying that they
OL,17,F"had a collision with the L'Ecume" and
OL,18,Fare "going to need immediate
OL,19,Fassistance".
