OL,3,CFerry horn only sounded seconds before
OL,4,Cdeadly impact, court told
OL,6,FThe prosecutor references a police
OL,7,Finterview with Mr Carr from 9 December
OL,8,F2022 - a day after the collision.
OL,10,FAdvocate Maletroit says Mr Carr is
OL,11,Fasked who he thought should give way
OL,12,Fas the two vessels approached and
OL,13,Fresponded, "My own ship was the give
OL,14,Fway vessel".
OL,16,FMr Carr and Mr Sevash-Zade both deny
OL,17,Fall the charges against them and the
OL,18,Fcase continues.
